Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Acute Rhinitis Market

Acute rhinitis market is expected to gain market growth in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research analyses the market is growing at a CAGR of 4.40% in the above-mentioned research forecast period. Increase in allergens throughout the world and increasing prevalence of respiratory diseases.

Technological advancements in order to enhance the efficacy of nasal sprays and easy availability of over the counter drugs also boost up the market growth. Moreover, increasing research and development and rising healthcare expenditure act as opportunity for the market growth. But, sometimes adverse effect caused by drugs, lack of skilled professionals, increasing adoption of alternative treatment and high presence of manufacturers engaged in manufacturing of generic drugs may hamper the global Acute rhinitis market.

Acute rhinitis is characterized as inflammation of nose which lasts only for few days. It typically caused due to virus infection. Acute rhinitis is mostly a type of non-allergic rhinitis which is confirmed by looking at some of symptoms including runny nose or postnasal strip, nasal congestion among others; however it can be caused due to allergies induced by bacteria or some other causative agents. In order to confirm whether it is acute rhinitis or chronic rhinitis doctors used to perform skin and blood test, nasal endoscopy, CT scan among others. The various types of treatment for acute rhinitis include saline, corticosteroid, antihistamines, anti-drip anticholinergic, and decongestants nasal sprays, among others.

As per the NCBI publication rhinoviruses are the most common pathogen responsible for acute rhinitis and their number is increasing in surrounding at a rapid rate. Approximately 50% of acute viral rhinitis caused due to rhinoviruses. Moreover in U.S approximately 19 million people are suffering from rhinitis, this affected population demands effective and novel drugs and therapies and hence expected to provide market with the lucrative growth.

